<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <%- include('partials/cache-control') %>
  <title><%= title %> | Healora</title>
  <link href="/images/Logo-browser.jpg" rel="icon">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --blue:       #1250b0;
      --blue-mid:   #1a6fd4;
      --sky:        #0ea5d4;
      --navy:       #071730;
      --ink:        #0f1f3d;
      --slate:      #475569;
      --muted:      #94a3b8;
      --border:     #e2e8f0;
      --surface:    #f8fafd;
      --white:      #ffffff;
      --accent:     #05c8a4;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--ink);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────
       HERO
    ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    .about-hero {
      position: relative;
      background: var(--navy);
      padding: 120px 0 80px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Geometric grid lines */
    .about-hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
    }

    /* Glow orb */
    .about-hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 600px; height: 600px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26,111,212,.35) 0%, transparent 70%);
      top: -200px; right: -150px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .hero-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: 6px 18px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero-pill i { font-size: 10px; }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    .hero-title em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--sky);
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.62);
      max-width: 500px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .hero-breadcrumb {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.4);
    }

    .hero-breadcrumb a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color .2s;
    }

    .hero-breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--white); }
    .hero-breadcrumb i { font-size: 8px; opacity: .7; }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────
       STATS FLOATING BAR
    ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    .stats-bar-wrap {
      margin-top: -36px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .stats-bar {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(7,23,48,.12), 0 1px 0 var(--border);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }

    .stat-cell {
      padding: 30px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
      position: relative;
    }

    .stat-cell:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .stat-cell::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%) scaleX(0);
      width: 40px; height: 20px;
      background: var(--blue-mid);
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: transform .3s;
    }

    .stat-cell:hover::after { transform: translateX(-50%) scaleX(1); }

    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--blue);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .stat-num sup {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .stat-lbl {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .8px;
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────
       COMMON SECTION ELEMENTS
    ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    .sec-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--blue-mid);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      background: #e8f1fb;
      padding: 5px 14px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .sec-title {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .sec-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--blue-mid); }

    .sec-body {
      font-size: 14.5px;
      color: var(--slate);
      line-height: 1.85;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────
       ABOUT SECTION
    ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    .about-section { padding: 100px 0; }

    .about-visual {
      position: relative;
    }

    .about-img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 20px;
      object-fit: cover;
      min-height: 460px;
      display: block;
      filter: brightness(.97) saturate(1.05);
    }

    /* Decorative frame behind image */
    .about-visual::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px; left: -20px;
      right: 20px; bottom: -20px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 22px;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .about-img { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    .about-text { padding-left: 32px; }

    .feature-chips {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 26px 0 32px;
    }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      background: var(--surface);
      color: var(--ink);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .chip i { color: var(--blue-mid); font-size: 11px; }

    .btn-primary-healora {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 13px 26px;
      background: var(--blue);
      color: var(--white);
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      transition: background .2s, transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
      letter-spacing: .2px;
    }

    .btn-primary-healora:hover {
      color: var(--white);
      background: var(--blue-mid);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(18,80,176,.3);
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────
       MISSION / VISION / VALUES  (dark card section)
    ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    .mission-section {
      background: var(--navy);
      padding: 90px 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .mission-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 48px 48px;
    }

    .mission-section .sec-tag {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      color: var(--accent);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
    }

    .mission-section .sec-title { color: var(--white); }
    .mission-section .sec-body  { color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); }

    .mission-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-top: 52px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .mission-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      padding: 40px 32px;
      transition: background .25s;
    }

    .mission-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.065); }

    .mc-num {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .mc-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 19px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .mc-blue   { background: rgba(26,111,212,.2); color: #60b0ff; }
    .mc-green  { background: rgba(5,200,164,.15); color: var(--accent); }
    .mc-purple { background: rgba(139,92,246,.2); color: #b69aff; }

    .mc-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .mc-desc {
      font-size: 13.5px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────
       CORE VALUES
    ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    .values-section { padding: 90px 0; background: var(--surface); }

    .values-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 52px;
    }

    .value-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 28px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 18px;
      transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s, transform .2s;
    }

    .value-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--blue-mid);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(18,80,176,.08);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .value-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .vi-blue   { background: #e8f1fb; color: var(--blue-mid); }
    .vi-green  { background: rgba(5,200,164,.1); color: #059669; }
    .vi-amber  { background: rgba(245,158,11,.1); color: #b45309; }
    .vi-purple { background: rgba(139,92,246,.1); color: #7c3aed; }

    .value-name {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .value-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--slate);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────
       CTA
    ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    .cta-section {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 90px 0;
    }

    .cta-inner {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0d3878 50%, #0d5a82 100%);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 64px 60px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 40px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .cta-inner::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 360px; height: 360px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14,165,212,.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
      right: -80px; top: -100px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .cta-inner::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
    }

    .cta-text { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    .cta-title {
      font-family: 'Lora', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .cta-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-weight: 300;
      max-width: 420px;
    }

    .cta-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .btn-cta-solid {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 13px 26px;
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--blue);
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all .2s;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-cta-solid:hover {
      background: #f0f6ff;
      color: var(--blue);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
    }

    .btn-cta-ghost {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 12px 26px;
      background: transparent;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all .2s;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-cta-ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────
       RESPONSIVE
    ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    @media (max-width: 991px) {
      .about-text { padding-left: 0; margin-top: 48px; }
      .about-visual::before { display: none; }
      .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .stat-cell:nth-child(2) { border-right: none; }
      .stat-cell { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .stat-cell:nth-child(3), .stat-cell:nth-child(4) { border-bottom: none; }
      .mission-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .cta-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 44px 36px; }
      .cta-actions { flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .about-hero { padding: 90px 0 60px; }
      .hero-title { font-size: 2rem; }
      .about-section, .values-section, .mission-section { padding: 70px 0; }
      .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .cta-inner { padding: 36px 24px; }
      .cta-actions { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/navbar') %>

<!-- ── Hero ── -->
<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-pill">
        <i class="fas fa-hospital-user"></i> About Healora
      </div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Where compassion meets<br><em>digital precision</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Building the future of healthcare with innovation, expertise,
        and an unwavering commitment to every patient's wellbeing.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-breadcrumb">
        <a href="/"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home</a>
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
        <span>About Us</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── Stats Bar ── -->
<div class="container stats-bar-wrap">
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-num">10<sup>+</sup></div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Years of Excellence</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-num">50<sup>+</sup></div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Expert Doctors</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-num">10K<sup>+</sup></div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Happy Patients</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell">
        <div class="stat-num">15<sup>+</sup></div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Awards Won</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── About Section ── -->
<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center g-5">

      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="about-visual">
          <img src="/images/about_us.jpg" alt="About Healora" class="about-img">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="about-text">
          <span class="sec-tag">Our Story</span>
          <h2 class="sec-title">Healing with <em>innovation</em><br>&amp; compassion</h2>
          <p class="sec-body" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
            At Healora Hospital, we're dedicated to providing world-class healthcare with compassion and innovation. Our team of expert doctors, nurses, and staff ensures the best treatment for every patient with advanced facilities and personalized care.
          </p>
          <p class="sec-body">
            We believe great healthcare is not just about treating illness — it's about building lasting relationships with our patients and their families, guiding them through every step of their health journey.
          </p>

          <div class="feature-chips">
            <span class="chip"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i> ISO Certified</span>
            <span class="chip"><i class="fas fa-award"></i> Award Winning</span>
            <span class="chip"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> 24/7 Emergency</span>
            <span class="chip"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Expert Team</span>
          </div>

          <a href="/doctors" class="btn-primary-healora">
            <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i> Meet Our Doctors
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── Mission / Vision / Values ── -->
<section class="mission-section">
  <div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:4px;">
      <span class="sec-tag">Our Foundation</span>
      <h2 class="sec-title" style="color:#fff;margin-top:8px;">Mission, Vision &amp; Values</h2>
      <p class="sec-body" style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);">
        The principles that guide everything we do at Healora
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mission-cards">
      <div class="mission-card">
        <div class="mc-num">01</div>
        <div class="mc-icon mc-blue"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
        <div class="mc-title">Our Mission</div>
        <p class="mc-desc">To deliver compassionate, high-quality healthcare with innovative technology that makes medical care accessible and efficient for every patient.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mission-card">
        <div class="mc-num">02</div>
        <div class="mc-icon mc-green"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i></div>
        <div class="mc-title">Our Vision</div>
        <p class="mc-desc">To be the most trusted healthcare system in the region — where every patient feels seen, heard, and cared for with dignity and respect.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mission-card">
        <div class="mc-num">03</div>
        <div class="mc-icon mc-purple"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i></div>
        <div class="mc-title">Our Values</div>
        <p class="mc-desc">Integrity, compassion, excellence, and innovation. We hold ourselves to the highest standards in every patient interaction and clinical outcome.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── Core Values ── -->
<section class="values-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center">
      <span class="sec-tag">What Drives Us</span>
      <h2 class="sec-title" style="margin-top:8px;">Our Core Values</h2>
      <p class="sec-body" style="max-width:460px;margin:0 auto;">
        Every decision we make is rooted in these fundamental principles
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon vi-blue"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i></div>
        <div>
          <div class="value-name">Patient-First Care</div>
          <p class="value-text">Every decision we make starts and ends with the patient. Their comfort, dignity, and recovery are always our top priority.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon vi-green"><i class="fas fa-microscope"></i></div>
        <div>
          <div class="value-name">Medical Excellence</div>
          <p class="value-text">We invest in the best technology and continuously train our staff to deliver outcomes that meet international standards.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon vi-amber"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
        <div>
          <div class="value-name">Trust &amp; Transparency</div>
          <p class="value-text">We build trust through honest communication, clear treatment plans, and respect for every patient's right to make informed decisions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon vi-purple"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i></div>
        <div>
          <div class="value-name">Continuous Innovation</div>
          <p class="value-text">We embrace technology and new methodologies to improve patient outcomes and make healthcare more accessible to everyone.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── CTA ── -->
<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <div class="cta-text">
        <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to experience better healthcare?</h2>
        <p class="cta-subtitle">
          Join thousands of patients who trust Healora for their healthcare needs.
